data.text:
New York: Triangle Books, 1943. Photoplay Edition. Hardcover. 300p. A hardcover book in good condition with a like dustjacket. The jacket has been taped to the book itself and is lightly worn. The pages of the book are deeply tanned with age, but otherwise, text clean and binding tight. Item #191093

Photoplay edition of THE COMMANDOS, published under the title of the movie adaptation. The dustjacket advertises the 1943 Columbia film starring Merle Oberon and Brian Aherne and directed by Dorothy Arzner.
